<title>USA: Colonial BancGroup ups div, splits stock.</title>
<headline>Colonial BancGroup ups div, splits stock.</headline>
<dateline>MONTGOMERY, Ala. 1997-01-15</dateline>
<text>
<p>Colonial BancGroup said Wednesday it is raising its dividend to $0.30 per share from $0.27 per share, payable February 11 to shareholders of record February 4.</p>
<p>The company said it will follow that a two-for-one stock split in the form of a 100 percent stock dividend, to be issuable February 11 to holders of record February 4.</p>
